    "To obtain the rephrased questions, we simply prompt GPT-4 using the instructions specified at the bottom of Tab. 7.",
    "We find the generated questions are quite good and only do small correction.",
    "Following popular methods, we first decode each video at 3 frames per second (fps) and then uniformly sample 32 video frames.",
    "We then feed all of the sampled 32 frames together with the question and answer into GPT-4o and prompt it to answer the question based on the sequence of image contents.",
    "Specific prompts are shown in Tab. 8."
